Package de.szut.dqi12.cheftrainer.connectorlib.messagetemplates

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommunityAutenticationAckMessage
    The CommunityAutenticationAckMessage is a Message Template to send the acknowledgment of an community registration or entering to the client.
    CommunityAuthenticationMessage
    The CommunityAuthenticationMessage should be used by the client.
    NewFormationMessage
    The NewFormationMessage should be used by the client application, when the user changes the Formation of his team.
    NewOfferMessage
    The NewOfferMessage should be used by the client application.
    NewPlayerOnMarketMessage
    This Message should be used, when a new Player should be added to the Market.
    SaveFormationAckMessage
    The SaveFormationAckMessage should be used by the server application to send the acknowledgement for a Formation change.
    SaveOfferAckMessage
    The SaveFormationAckMessage should be used by the server application to send the acknowledgement for a Formation change.
    TransactionMessage
    The TransactionMessage should be used by the client application.
    UserAuthenticationAckMessage
    The UserAuthenticationAckMessage is used by the server application to inform the client application.
    UserAuthenticationMessage
    The UserAuthenticationMessage should be used, when a user wants to login or registrate to the server.
    UserCommunityListMessage
    The UserCommunityListMessage is used by the server application.
